<item>
            <title>[LU-11179] enable neterror to console by default</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11179</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should enable the &lt;tt&gt;neterror&lt;/tt&gt; debugging mask by default in &lt;tt&gt;libcfs_debug&lt;/tt&gt; so that we can more easily identify cases where there are network problems causing Lustre issues.  Otherwise, I think we are missing cases where the underlying network is unstable, and we are seeing effects at the Lustre level that are hard to debug.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
